reviewText: Contents: SILK RIBBON STITCHES (25 minutes): Running Whip Stitch, Lazy Daisy, Straight Stitch, Japanese Ribbon Stitch, Loop Stitch, Spider Web Rose, Twisted Rose, Knots, Cascading, Feather Stitch, Fly Stitch.
